Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:34.72,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:39.62,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仅仅三秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:42.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我已经坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:14.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}在c'est la vie三位歌手当中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:17.82,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}虽比我稍逊色一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:20.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}但感性的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:22.13,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}金昌模
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那么 下一位是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:31.34,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}散发着夜来香的长发美女和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:33.64,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}系着黄丝巾的美女点的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:35.54,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:37.54,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:40.95,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我唱得嗓子都快要出血了\N也不会有那种反应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.95,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这小子只凭一张脸蛋就...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}-最近流行的\N-真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:52.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:56.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}爱情故事的歌曲当中最红的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:59.06,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}从哪里开始讲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.37,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}她的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.61,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}第一眼就被迷住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:21.95,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}晚上见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.15,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}应该在工作室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:31.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}最近成天待在工作室里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:32.66,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这也是你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:36.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}厚脸皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.66,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.47,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}听说你俩今天再比一把
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.97,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}他和仁河吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.97,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}到现在十胜十一败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}应该算是雪耻战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:47.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这次是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.17,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}赌什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:50.88,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.28,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:55.18,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你们两个真是 为了女的比试一场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:58.08,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}比起我 是仁河那小子彻底被迷上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.49,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}咦 不会吧\N咦 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.49,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河哥 哪来的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.09,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:06.49,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我和他一起住了三年宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.89,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}压根都没看见 他靠近过女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:09.70,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.40,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}就算把仁河哥和女人\N单独放到无人岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河哥也不会和女人搭讪的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.80,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊哈 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这回仁河真的是一见钟情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.61,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}突然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:11.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}心开始狂跳起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.93,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.44,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.34,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:52.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}各位学生 请停止活动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.16,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}立正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.36,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}向着国旗 敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:19.38,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我面对自豪的太极旗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:24.69,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}郑重宣誓要献出自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:31.20,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}忠于祖国和民族的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}说起来很可笑 当时我想着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.10,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我来到这世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.21,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是为了奉献自己的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:43.31,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}好好去爱那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.89,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}金允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.30,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这不是日记本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.30,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.21,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么傻站着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.41,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:26.41,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喂 你现在不是这么悠闲的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:31.02,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}咱们的恋人到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.12,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哦 到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.32,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}要比一场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.14,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河哥哥 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.74,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你为什么一直站在仁河那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:57.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}因为东旭哥哥\N要抢仁河哥哥先看上的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.94,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不是说一起打的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.15,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:04.45,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}东旭哥哥专门学仁河喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}允熙 掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.07,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}徐仁河 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.68,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}徐仁河 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.78,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}徐仁河吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.40,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}今天怎么这么倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.91,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}日记本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.62,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}天啊 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.33,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喂 干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.13,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}错过她几次的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:30.74,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我已经坠入爱河了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.54,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.04,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.34,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.74,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:37.04,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}放手放手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}让 让我撒个尿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:41.45,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喂喂喂 怎么可以在这里撒尿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}撒泡尿就走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:46.65,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}金允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:57.02,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}咦 Love Story
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:05.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}爱就是永远不必说抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}去世的爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.44,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喜欢的爱情电影故事中的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:16.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}但我还不知道这句话的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:19.04,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}原来父母都去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.69,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:18.30,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个 你昨天有没有看到我的日记本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:22.51,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不是 看到黄色的本子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不可以让别人看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:28.41,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:34.62,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 你应该很忙吧 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.42,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:52.14,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.34,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}金允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:56.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}过得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.84,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}上次...等一下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:00.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}给我一点时间 就一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.55,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}就聊一会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.45,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}金允熙 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.45,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}为什么拒绝我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.15,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}嗯 仁河
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.66,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不会耽误你太多时间 一会就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.06,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}她又有男生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我真的喜欢金允熙你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:19.06,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哇 好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.77,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是你们系的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.97,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}嗯 是我们系的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:25.17,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}但是和她不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是我讨厌的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.88,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 她就是你们系的麦当娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.88,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哇 麦当娜\N麦当娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.88,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真是 她算什么麦当娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.08,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}如果是你讨厌的人\N人气就应该比你高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.99,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我经常听说你们系的麦当娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.29,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}她的人气应该很高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.59,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}就在男生里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:49.09,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 清纯 又文静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.50,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}独来独往又高傲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.10,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}在男生里面人气最高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.20,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}但是一个朋友都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.70,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}又很果断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.11,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}加上又这么善良
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.51,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}太赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.51,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}三秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:13.72,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:18.32,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}难得这么早来 去上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:22.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}看一下幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:26.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这是约翰内斯 维米尔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}他将宁静又严肃的日常瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.84,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}利用非常细腻的质感和光线...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:36.34,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}爱是永远不必说抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.04,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}去世的爸爸和妈妈喜欢的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:42.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}《 Love Story》中的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:47.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}但我还不知道这句话的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:53.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}时隔10年Love Story要重新上映了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:57.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这次我真的好想看这部电影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:09.17,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}秋天里的美术大学建筑前的长凳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.58,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是我最喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:16.88,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}今天不知道为什么这个位子让我心动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:37.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}如果我有伤口 奶奶一直帮我涂口水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:43.31,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这样的话 痛的地方真的会痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:49.51,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我现在知道了 那是奶奶对我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:59.73,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}奶奶说过\N人有两只手是为了拥抱你爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:06.03,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我总有一天也会像电影里的主角一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:09.84,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}和去世的父母一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:13.34,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那样遇见我爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:19.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我反覆读着日记到深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:25.45,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}去世的爸爸最喜欢的小王子中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:29.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}有“如果喜欢我的话 就驯养我”的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:36.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}爱情可能就是这样相互了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:46.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我想要更了解她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.65,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这是你借的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}允熙 允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个人不是徐仁河吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.17,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你认识那个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.48,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}没 没有很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:33.18,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:36.68,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你真的不认识\N那有名的c'est la vie三人帮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:37.68,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:38.78,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:40.49,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}过来 你好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.79,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:44.99,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}首先 DJ李东旭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.59,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}外号是花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:50.90,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是优等生又是大医院家的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:55.40,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}长得帅 有能力 加上性格又好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:58.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以呀 很多女生都喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:01.11,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}第二个是金昌模
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:03.71,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}外号 大寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:06.51,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}出身乡下 兄弟又多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:09.72,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以 每天都像饿死鬼投胎一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:13.12,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}但是 只要开始唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:16.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那样子 帅得让人都会原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:21.93,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}然后是 最重要的人 徐仁河
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:27.13,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}神秘的外貌下\N既温柔又有个性的美大生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:29.13,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}正所谓是个王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:32.54,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}三人中 担当作词作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:34.64,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}拥有足以得奖的画技
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:36.94,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是有艺术细胞的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:40.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}还有啊 听说家世也相当好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:44.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}在那附近的人 想要走路的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:46.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是不得不踩上他们的墙角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:49.45,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}还有 因为是化导非常惊人的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:51.06,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}听说 还有未婚妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:53.16,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:57.66,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的说有未婚妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:22:59.66,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:07.77,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我没有未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:15.78,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:18.18,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}为什么那样对我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:20.99,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}说 没有未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:23.39,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}难道对我有意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:29.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.06,0:24:35.56,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}请你稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.58,0:24:58.98,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}前辈 有没有伞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.39,0:26:51.50,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.59,0:27:14.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.12,0:27:17.52,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}刚才 不是我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.22,0:27:21.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个未婚妻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.83,0:27:25.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.23,0:27:27.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我没有未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.44,0:27:38.04,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我知道 那话不是你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.05,0:27:41.65,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.96,0:27:58.36,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我 我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.06,0:28:01.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我也不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.57,0:28:10.98,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这样的话 你再往里靠一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.32,0:28:57.52,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你喜欢它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.93,0:29:02.53,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}雨
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.93,0:29:04.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你喜欢雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.93,0:29:09.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 是 我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.24,0:29:15.14,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}看到雨的话 即伤感 又幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.14,0:29:18.14,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哈 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.65,0:29:28.75,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}刚才那本书
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.75,0:29:31.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 那个小王子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.46,0:29:37.36,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那本书作者的诗里 有这样一句
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.76,0:29:43.87,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}爱情 有着幸福与悲伤的双面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.67,0:29:49.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}爱情与雨 感觉它们很像
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.68,0:30:01.49,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你还好吧\N你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.99,0:30:09.70,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你撑着这把伞 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.00,0:30:20.41,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个 我 突然想起来 我约了人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.41,0:30:24.91,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.01,0:30:34.92,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这伞 我什么时候还你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.12,0:30:40.03,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.63,0:30:44.73,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这周日 你有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.23,0:30:46.53,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.64,0:30:57.84,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个 电影
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.64,0:31:00.15,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.65,0:31:03.65,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}Love Story
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.55,0:31:07.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我原本就特别想看Love Story呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.26,0:31:17.16,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那 要一起去看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.17,0:31:28.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.18,0:31:38.98,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那伞 是在图书馆捡的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.98,0:31:40.19,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.95,0:32:44.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}都快要淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.45,0:32:51.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你要不要 和我换一下雨伞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.96,0:32:52.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.86,0:32:54.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哎呦 全湿透了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.26,0:32:57.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}伞也完全坏掉了 和我换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.96,0:33:01.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不用了 我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.77,0:33:09.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不然 就先擦一擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.67,0:33:13.08,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.78,0:33:20.59,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不过 你不认识我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.49,0:33:34.20,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 前几天在网球场见过的那位...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.20,0:33:38.80,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哎 不是 那不是我们俩第一回见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:41.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.41,0:33:51.42,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哎呦 还真是伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.42,0:33:54.42,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是家政系的学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.42,0:33:55.62,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.62,0:33:58.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我有个关系不错的弟弟也是那的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.22,0:34:01.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}在学校也见过几回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.73,0:34:06.73,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}看样子你很喜欢电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.73,0:34:09.93,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}就只是随便看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.93,0:34:12.94,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}想看《Love Story》来着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.94,0:34:16.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}要一起看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.34,0:34:22.65,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}初次见面的男女一起看电影\N有点困难是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.65,0:34:26.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那么 下次怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.05,0:34:29.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}如果下次再次偶然碰到的话\N就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.96,0:34:30.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.86,0:34:34.16,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我是说电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.16,0:34:35.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.96,0:34:38.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你得坐这趟公车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.47,0:34:46.87,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}快上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.31,0:35:29.31,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}在这样的下雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.31,0:35:32.52,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}献给像我一样坠入爱情的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.52,0:35:35.82,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喂 他在说什么坠入爱情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.82,0:35:36.72,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}有什么大惊小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.72,0:35:40.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}-再次遇到你爱着的人...\N-东旭这样又不是一天两天了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.83,0:35:42.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}I'll be waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.83,0:35:45.93,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}在最好的偶像 为您奉上
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.90,0:36:52.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.60,0:36:54.80,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.00,0:37:00.71,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}陪我喝点酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.71,0:37:03.01,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.01,0:37:06.61,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哎呦 在作曲中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.61,0:37:08.51,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}随便弄弄
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.51,0:37:12.32,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不错啊 你快点完成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.32,0:37:14.82,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}之后就可以在电台公开节目上唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.82,0:37:18.62,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}算了吧 怪丢人的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.52,0:37:23.03,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}徐仁河 你给我说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.03,0:37:24.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.83,0:37:29.94,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个三秒 你上次说的那个三秒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.94,0:37:34.84,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}命运的伴侣 是不是找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.84,0:37:39.44,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以你才在这作曲什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.44,0:37:41.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哈哈 真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.05,0:37:43.65,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.65,0:37:46.35,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我们还果真是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.35,0:37:49.15,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.15,0:37:50.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我也找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.96,0:37:52.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.26,0:37:54.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}三秒钟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.76,0:37:57.36,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.58,0:38:19.58,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.58,0:38:24.29,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你的手流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.09,0:38:31.20,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.20,0:38:35.20,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}实习的时候不小心烫了一下 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.20,0:38:37.90,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}给你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.11,0:38:49.51,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.64,0:39:16.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那样帮我处理伤口的人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.24,0:39:19.64,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}除了小时候我妈之外 她是第一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.64,0:39:22.75,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是因为她长得像妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.35,0:39:27.55,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.55,0:39:33.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}-啊 -"Love Story" 是要一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.26,0:39:34.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哎 真羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.76,0:39:37.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我被拒绝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.86,0:39:39.87,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}但还是死皮赖脸的和她说
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.87,0:39:42.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}下次遇见的话再一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.27,0:39:44.97,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以说不管怎么样也得偶然遇上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.97,0:39:47.97,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}还真是愁人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.57,0:39:52.68,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}一样的电影 还真的巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.68,0:39:58.98,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}Love means...never...sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.98,0:40:03.79,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不过女生们怎么就这么喜欢这句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.79,0:40:12.50,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}大概是因为 爱情是真心付出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.50,0:40:15.30,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是因为知道彼此的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.30,0:40:18.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以不用说对不起这句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.00,0:40:23.71,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是哦 我要是女生的话绝对会喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.71,0:40:26.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我要是女生的话 绝对不会喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.81,0:40:29.31,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.02,0:40:35.32,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.32,0:40:40.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}图书馆四层的诗集的角落位置
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.73,0:40:46.93,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}满天星
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.13,0:40:51.44,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}圣埃克苏佩里的《小王子》
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.44,0:40:57.94,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}发条钟和李斯特的《觉悟》
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.87,0:41:29.47,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喂 不是 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.47,0:41:31.48,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}都说去了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.48,0:41:32.58,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.58,0:41:34.08,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你连从来不穿的西装都穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.08,0:41:35.28,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这到底是要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.28,0:41:37.78,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我都把我爸的西装借来了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.78,0:41:39.28,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}总之先一起过去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.28,0:41:41.09,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}到底是要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.09,0:41:42.49,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}-走吧 -走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.49,0:41:44.99,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}好了 好了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.19,0:41:49.80,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你说联谊中谁会来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.80,0:41:50.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.60,0:41:53.20,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我都说了 不管怎样都会偶然遇见的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.20,0:41:55.70,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}都说了要一起去看电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.70,0:41:59.20,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以说 要在联谊中"偶然"遇到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.20,0:42:03.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是啊 在这历史的一刻\N怎么能没有你和昌模呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.81,0:42:06.41,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}进去吧 先坐那边
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.41,0:42:07.11,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}过来过来 坐这边
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.11,0:42:10.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}推什么你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.22,0:42:12.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喂 你之前知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.22,0:42:15.12,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这小子在哪勾搭的妹子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.12,0:42:17.92,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不好意思啦 我先出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.92,0:42:21.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}今天就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.53,0:42:26.33,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你认识吗 把他弄成这熊样的那女生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.33,0:42:27.93,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我也很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.93,0:42:31.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.24,0:42:34.94,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}好像说和慧静是一个系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.14,0:42:41.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你说家政系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.05,0:42:43.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}他为了这个联谊求了慧静好几天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.05,0:42:47.75,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}来的会是什么样的女生们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.05,0:42:53.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}如果我说\N有钱短命的女生是理想型的话
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.96,0:42:57.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}会不会挨揍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.26,0:42:58.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不会是...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.26,0:43:01.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}对了 那个麦当娜
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.67,0:43:03.07,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你说谁
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.07,0:43:05.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}就是慧静特别讨厌的那个麦当娜
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.27,0:43:06.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是那个女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.57,0:43:09.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你原来不是特别讨厌那个女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.27,0:43:11.98,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这个嘛 来了你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.98,0:43:14.88,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哥哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.28,0:43:19.28,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}慧静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.59,0:43:24.89,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我们没迟到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.89,0:43:30.30,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这边 连我们系的系花都请来了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.90,0:43:37.20,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}还有本来要去图书馆的朋友们 都拽来了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.21,0:43:50.42,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}终于见面了 徐仁河前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.42,0:43:53.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}见到你真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.52,0:44:00.63,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我们又在这里偶遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.33,0:44:04.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我们是不是应该去看电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.23,0:44:05.53,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.14,0:44:11.94,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}简单的介绍一下我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.94,0:44:14.44,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}如果把我爸爸的名字说出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.44,0:44:17.74,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}以后再也不能去那样的公司上班
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.74,0:44:21.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}只是想让大家看到我真实的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.05,0:44:22.65,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}就不说这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.95,0:44:29.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}比起其它的 我最喜欢的就是美术
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.76,0:44:36.56,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}未来的理想是当画家的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.07,0:44:44.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.27,0:44:50.28,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那么最后该金允熙了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.78,0:45:02.09,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}大家好\N我是家政系二年级学生金允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.39,0:45:04.79,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}见到各位很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.29,0:45:07.49,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}见到你 我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.69,0:45:10.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.80,0:45:14.40,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}对了 刚才说的电影是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.80,0:45:17.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你们俩约好去看电影了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.50,0:45:21.11,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}以前见过一次面
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.11,0:45:25.01,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}如果再偶然遇到的话\N就去看Love Story
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.31,0:45:26.71,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.71,0:45:28.41,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.41,0:45:30.82,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.82,0:45:34.72,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我要是也能一起去看\NLove Story就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.52,0:45:38.52,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我是一点都不想看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.52,0:45:42.33,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.33,0:45:44.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}"爱就是永远不必说抱歉"\N这句话是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.43,0:45:45.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.73,0:45:51.44,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}因为爱是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.44,0:45:56.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}互相知道对方的真心\N所以不需要感到抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.45,0:46:02.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.15,0:46:08.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.85,0:46:10.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}被感动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.86,0:46:14.66,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么 你们两人这么快就相通了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.66,0:46:18.16,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么可以这么快就看对眼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.67,0:46:24.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}现在开始决定搭挡
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.27,0:46:26.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}男生已经拿出了物品
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.27,0:46:29.17,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}女生们只要进行选择就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.17,0:46:30.38,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}首先...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.38,0:46:33.98,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这个 是仁河的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.48,0:46:37.68,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}有人借走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.69,0:46:46.59,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我的损失更大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.59,0:46:49.29,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}第一对搭挡是昌模与仁淑
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.29,0:46:51.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.00,0:46:54.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喂 这样就决定搭挡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.00,0:46:55.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真倒霉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.60,0:46:57.50,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.60,0:47:01.71,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那么下面是允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.01,0:47:05.21,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.24,0:47:34.34,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这是我的啊 看来我们真的有缘份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.85,0:47:51.36,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}对于那个女孩我应该说什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.36,0:48:00.17,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}她是发条钟 是满天星\N是圣埃克苏佩里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.47,0:48:03.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喜欢那首叫做《觉悟》的诗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.87,0:48:08.87,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}而且她是我朋友喜欢的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.18,0:48:19.18,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个时节我因为她而感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.39,0:48:24.09,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}谢谢 这是我最喜欢的花
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.39,0:48:27.99,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}也因为她而感到伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.80,0:48:38.90,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河讨厌谁
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.90,0:48:41.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河最近聚会也不来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.81,0:48:44.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}每天都很早就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.81,0:48:46.11,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.81,0:48:51.82,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你不觉得他是在躲允熙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.82,0:48:54.32,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河为什么要躲允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.32,0:48:55.52,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.62,0:49:01.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}难道是允熙以为仁河喜欢她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.13,0:49:03.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.83,0:49:09.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以觉得尴尬的仁河就会躲着允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.43,0:49:12.44,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}没错 没错就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.44,0:49:13.94,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.94,0:49:16.14,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我觉得所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.64,0:49:19.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}允熙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.15,0:49:23.15,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.65,0:49:29.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这个裂开了应该不会坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.26,0:49:34.46,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我觉得你是最了解允熙的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.46,0:49:38.16,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我怎么会了解
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.46,0:49:40.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}跟你挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.67,0:49:42.47,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你说的她都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.07,0:49:48.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}她喜欢那个Love Story\N也喜欢满天星
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.58,0:49:51.78,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不是你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.78,0:49:54.38,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不要这样 帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.38,0:49:55.78,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}如果这节日还没有给她
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.78,0:49:58.58,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}以后可能就要一直做朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.59,0:50:11.90,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不要给了\N只要让她看到真心不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.30,0:50:14.50,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那到底真心是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.80,0:50:19.50,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我怎么会知道 又不是我喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.21,0:50:23.01,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.22,0:50:33.42,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我去上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.52,0:50:36.02,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.93,0:50:42.33,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}偷偷的吃真要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.33,0:50:44.13,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}应该光明正大的吃
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.13,0:50:46.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.53,0:50:51.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}都说偷吃的东西最好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.24,0:50:52.64,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.44,0:50:57.84,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.84,0:50:59.54,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你小子被我抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.54,0:51:02.05,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}别这样 我可是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.65,0:51:04.15,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}慧静啊 我们去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.15,0:51:06.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我要去上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.25,0:51:07.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}允熙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.25,0:51:08.15,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.55,0:51:10.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.36,0:51:13.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.87,0:51:26.37,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}小姐 你这个不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.37,0:51:27.47,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你超了几厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.47,0:51:28.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}反正是超了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.09,0:51:44.79,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}还以为会被抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.79,0:51:48.09,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}朴仁淑真受不了你的小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.09,0:51:50.10,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么不用在学习上
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.10,0:51:51.90,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}被抓到会麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.30,0:51:55.40,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}TAXI
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.21,0:52:01.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}东旭怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.31,0:52:05.51,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你知道东旭喜欢你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.31,0:52:08.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}说这话不是让你有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.81,0:52:12.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不过他对你好像是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.42,0:52:19.73,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}说那句话的时候很喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.73,0:52:23.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}爱情是真心这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.83,0:52:28.53,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以不需要觉得抱歉这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.53,0:52:31.34,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}嗯 Love Story
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.34,0:52:32.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.94,0:52:39.14,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}跟我像是一类人 所以喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.75,0:52:40.95,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.95,0:52:46.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}听了仁淑的话我有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.15,0:52:48.45,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.45,0:52:54.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我怕你和仁河之间真的有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.96,0:52:56.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我其实...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.17,0:53:02.77,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喜欢仁河
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.37,0:53:06.77,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.27,0:53:09.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}就连仁淑也不能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.68,0:53:16.68,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河说有一个只画自己妻子的画家
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.38,0:53:20.89,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}因为不想画人物 所以这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.89,0:53:22.69,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河说他也想这样
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.99,0:53:28.09,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河应该只会画爱的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.90,0:53:34.80,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我一定会让仁河画我的画像
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.23,0:54:02.63,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}换个姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.14,0:54:12.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}手臂也要换
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.14,0:54:19.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}好好收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.15,0:54:24.75,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怎么都给扒光了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.75,0:54:27.55,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真是让人无语问青天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.96,0:54:30.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.46,0:54:33.46,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}该不会是耍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.46,0:54:35.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我说 这真的是传统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.86,0:54:37.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这样都脱个精光也是传统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.86,0:54:39.06,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.87,0:54:40.87,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那女的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.87,0:54:42.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}女的也全脱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.27,0:54:44.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}当然了 是模特儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.17,0:54:47.47,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.47,0:54:49.37,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那女人的 胸部 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.37,0:54:50.48,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.48,0:54:53.28,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}全都脱光了让人画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.18,0:54:55.58,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.58,0:54:58.08,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河也有可能画那个的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.88,0:55:01.09,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这小子自己享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.70,0:55:12.80,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.00,0:55:21.51,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}这不是允熙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.01,0:55:25.61,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}允熙的画怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.22,0:55:31.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.22,0:55:34.42,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我干嘛生气
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.92,0:55:36.32,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.32,0:55:38.42,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你喜欢的那个真心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.42,0:55:40.53,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我用真心对待她就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.53,0:55:42.43,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你不满意的就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.93,0:55:44.63,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}怕我伤害她
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.23,0:55:47.83,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.83,0:55:49.33,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.33,0:55:50.74,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.14,0:55:55.84,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你本来就不喜欢\N我跟女人见面的这些方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.14,0:56:00.25,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}但是我这次是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.25,0:56:02.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的 相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.05,0:56:07.75,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哦 你那个女人怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.25,0:56:13.16,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个3秒 你之后还遇过那个女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.86,0:56:17.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个女人 我放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.66,0:56:18.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.97,0:56:23.77,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}除了我 她有了别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.77,0:56:26.57,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么啊 所以说你就放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.57,0:56:28.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}也不打一架
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.77,0:56:32.78,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不能打 也不想打
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.98,0:56:40.89,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那是可以让我直接说出心里话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.49,0:56:45.89,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.39,0:56:51.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}喂 你什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.60,0:56:52.60,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河哥
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.40,0:56:54.70,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.20,0:56:58.50,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你又去买东西了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.41,0:57:04.21,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}天气真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.21,0:57:05.91,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不然就这么出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.91,0:57:07.91,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}真的啊 去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.91,0:57:09.92,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}跟着我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.92,0:57:13.82,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个 我得先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.82,0:57:15.32,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}上第三节课
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.32,0:57:19.52,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河哥 是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.13,0:57:21.33,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.23,0:57:25.33,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河哥 你跟允熙在一起不方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.73,0:57:28.23,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.83,0:57:30.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}慧静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.04,0:57:32.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.64,0:57:38.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁淑说\N有允熙在的聚会 仁河哥都不参加
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.24,0:57:39.95,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}就像躲着她一样
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.95,0:57:42.15,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}什么啊 不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.15,0:57:44.35,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河为什么要躲着允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.35,0:57:45.85,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.16,0:57:55.36,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那个 我也要回去上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.36,0:57:56.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.76,0:57:58.26,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}走了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.67,0:58:03.37,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你没事说什么废话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.47,0:58:11.18,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你该不会真的不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.28,0:58:14.08,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我怎么会不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.48,0:58:16.58,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}她是东旭喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.58,0:58:18.08,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.40,0:58:37.20,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}现在 我觉得真的不能再这样下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.03,0:59:07.63,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}没带伞出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.43,0:59:11.54,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.54,0:59:15.84,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我等朋友 然后一起用就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.74,0:59:18.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.06,0:59:36.86,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}别等朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.86,0:59:38.66,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}用这个走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.08,0:59:51.68,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}最近为什么不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.98,0:59:55.78,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.88,1:00:03.89,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.89,1:00:09.19,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}如果仁河你因为我而缺席聚会的话
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.19,1:00:13.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那还是我缺席比较好一点
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.10,1:00:16.10,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}谁说的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.10,1:00:18.10,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我只是有点忙而已
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.41,1:00:26.01,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}所以 你是因为那个才不出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.91,1:00:30.72,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}没必要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.72,1:00:34.22,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我怎么会那么在乎你呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.62,1:00:38.82,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你好像跟东旭相处的不错
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.82,1:00:40.33,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}看起来很好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.73,1:00:47.93,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}东旭和我 还不是那种关系
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.34,1:00:54.24,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那我重说
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.14,1:00:58.34,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你们如果能好好发展就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.54,1:01:03.65,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}还有 以后我们也好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.96,1:01:13.16,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}下次聚会一定要来
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.16,1:01:16.76,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那时候见吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.10,1:01:58.00,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我觉得会有所不同的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.51,1:02:08.81,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}只要我自己改变
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.12,1:02:13.92,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我们就可以毫无芥蒂的相处
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.22,1:02:17.12,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我那样认为的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.46,1:02:55.56,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}下 集 预 告
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.56,1:02:57.66,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}你到现在为止交往的女人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.66,1:02:58.96,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}哪里和允熙不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.96,1:03:00.77,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不要一直生气了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.77,1:03:02.47,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}今天气氛也不错
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.47,1:03:03.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}不如就直接点吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.67,1:03:05.17,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}用怕伤害人的藉口
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.17,1:03:06.67,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}如果因为这个而无法开口
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.67,1:03:08.27,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那就不是藉口了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.27,1:03:10.38,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.38,1:03:12.98,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.68,1:03:15.28,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.28,1:03:18.28,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}仁河只会画他爱的人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.08,1:03:21.49,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}那些画 没有别的意义
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.49,1:03:23.99,Default Drama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\b2}对我来说只是风景而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.28,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,家政系 金允熙
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.89,0:40:07.99,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,(爱就是永远不必说抱歉)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.93,0:24:48.67,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}你和我 曾有属于我们的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.67,0:25:01.89,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}你和我 曾秘密的相见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.45,0:25:14.27,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}你和我 互相倾慕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.23,0:25:26.78,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}你和我 要开始相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.11,0:25:33.65,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}但是 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.55,0:25:39.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}没有那个你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.59,0:26:18.06,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}遇见了你 我无比幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.33,0:26:25.27,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}如果你笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.74,0:26:31.74,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}我也跟着一起笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.14,0:26:37.85,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}如果你悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.32,0:26:44.39,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}我们两人一同哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.86,0:26:57.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}你和我 要开始相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.45,0:28:21.79,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}来 闭眼倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.79,0:28:25.79,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}透明的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.79,0:28:31.43,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}代替我在你耳边说爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.43,0:28:38.57,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}喃喃羞涩的这首歌回荡在街道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.57,0:28:46.24,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}小小的雨伞下 像恋人一般牵着你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.24,0:28:49.82,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}走去哪里都好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.82,0:28:54.39,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}即使全身湿透也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.39,0:29:02.53,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}爱情如雨 像温柔的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.53,0:29:05.10,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}让我做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.10,0:29:10.94,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}闭上眼睛的任何角落 都只看得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.94,0:29:18.71,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}慢慢走过去 今天要开口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.71,0:29:25.65,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}落下的雨滴 是否可以承载我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.65,0:29:30.66,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}但愿那雨滴是我的嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.00,0:29:43.17,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}闭上眼睛去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.17,0:29:47.31,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}轻轻靠在我的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.31,0:29:51.31,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur9}悄悄亲在熟睡的你的脸颊上...


